{"id":175,"parent_id":172,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":175,"title":"Galatians 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"Gal.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","God gave the gospel to Abraham—The Mosaic law was added because of transgressions—The law was a schoolmaster until Christ—The Saints are children of God by faith—All who are of the faith and baptized into Christ become Abraham’s seed."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.1","order":"03.11.003.19524"},["b","1"],"O foolish Galatians, who hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"bewitched"],"you, that ye should not obey the truth, before whose eyes Jesus Christ hath been evidently set forth, crucified among you?"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.2","order":"03.11.003.19525"},["b","2"],"This only would I learn of you, Received ye the Spirit by the works of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"law"],", or by the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"hearing"],"of faith?"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.3","order":"03.11.003.19526"},["b","3"],"Are ye so foolish? having begun in the Spirit, are ye now made perfect by the flesh?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.4","order":"03.11.003.19527"},["b","4"],"Have ye suffered so many things in vain? if",["i","it be"],"yet in vain."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.5","order":"03.11.003.19528"},["b","5"],"He therefore that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"ministereth"],"to you the Spirit, and worketh miracles among you,",["i","doeth he it"],"by the works of the law, or by the hearing of faith?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.6","order":"03.11.003.19529"},["b","6"],"Even as Abraham believed God, and it was accounted to him for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.7","order":"03.11.003.19530"},["b","7"],"Know ye therefore that they which are of faith, the same are the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"children of Abraham"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.8","order":"03.11.003.19531"},["b","8"],"And the scripture, foreseeing that God would justify the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"heathen"],"through faith, preached before the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"gospel"],"unto Abraham,",["i","saying,"],"In thee shall all",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"nations"],"be",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"blessed"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.9","order":"03.11.003.19532"},["b","9"],"So then they which be of faith are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"blessed"],"with faithful Abraham."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.10","order":"03.11.003.19533"},["b","10"],"For as many as are of the works of the law are under the curse: for it is written,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Cursed"],["i","is"],"every one that continueth not in all things which are written in the book of the law to do them."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.11","order":"03.11.003.19534"},["b","11"],"But that no man is justified by the law in the sight of God,",["i","it is"],"evident: for, The just shall live by",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.12","order":"03.11.003.19535"},["b","12"],"And the law is not of faith: but, The man that doeth them shall live in them."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.13","order":"03.11.003.19536"},["b","13"],"Christ hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"redeemed"],"us from the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"curse"],"of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"law"],", being made a curse for us: for it is written,",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_13d"},"Cursed"],["i","is"],"every one that hangeth on a tree:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.14","order":"03.11.003.19537"},["b","14"],"That the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"blessing"],"of Abraham might come on the Gentiles through",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"Jesus Christ"],"; that we might receive the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"promise"],"of the Spirit through faith."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.15","order":"03.11.003.19538"},["b","15"],"Brethren, I speak after the manner of men; Though",["i","it be"],"but a man’s covenant, yet",["i","if it be"],"confirmed, no man disannulleth, or addeth thereto."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.16","order":"03.11.003.19539"},["b","16"],"Now to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Abraham"],"and his seed were the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"promises"],"made. He saith not, And to seeds, as of many; but as of one, And to thy seed, which is Christ."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.17","order":"03.11.003.19540"},["b","17"],"And this I say,",["i","that"],"the covenant, that was confirmed before of God in Christ, the law, which was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"four hundred and thirty"],"years after, cannot disannul, that it should make the promise of none effect."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.18","order":"03.11.003.19541"},["b","18"],"For if the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"inheritance"],["i","be"],"of the law,",["i","it is"],"no more of promise: but God gave",["i","it"],"to Abraham by promise."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.19","order":"03.11.003.19542"},["b","19"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Wherefore"],"then",["i","serveth"],"the law? It was",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"added"],"because of transgressions, till the seed should come to whom the promise was made;",["i","and it was"],"ordained by angels in the hand of a mediator."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.20","order":"03.11.003.19543"},["b","20"],"Now a mediator is not",["i","a mediator"],"of one, but God is one."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.21","order":"03.11.003.19544"},["b","21"],["i","Is"],"the law then against the promises of God? God forbid: for if there had been a law given which could have given life, verily righteousness should have been by the law."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.22","order":"03.11.003.19545"},["b","22"],"But the scripture hath concluded all under",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"sin"],", that the promise by faith of Jesus Christ might be given to them that believe."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.23","order":"03.11.003.19546"},["b","23"],"But before faith came, we were kept under the law, shut up unto the faith which should afterwards be revealed."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.24","order":"03.11.003.19547"},["b","24"],"Wherefore the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"law"],"was our",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"schoolmaster"],["i","to bring us"],"unto Christ, that we might be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_24c"},"justified"],"by faith."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.25","order":"03.11.003.19548"},["b","25"],"But after that faith is come, we are no longer under a schoolmaster."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.26","order":"03.11.003.19549"},["b","26"],"For ye are all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"children"],"of God by",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"faith"],"in Christ Jesus."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.27","order":"03.11.003.19550"},["b","27"],"For as many of you as have been",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"baptized"],"into Christ have put on Christ."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.28","order":"03.11.003.19551"},["b","28"],"There is neither Jew nor",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"Greek"],", there is neither bond nor free, there is neither male nor female: for ye are all",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"one"],"in Christ Jesus."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.29","order":"03.11.003.19552"},["b","29"],"And if ye",["i","be"],"Christ’s, then are ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"Abraham’s"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_29b"},"seed"],", and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_29c"},"heirs"],"according to the promise."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.1a","order":"03.11.003.19553"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/7.18.16-18"},"Jacob 7:18 (16–18)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-the-early-christian-church"},"TG Apostasy of the Early Christian Church"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.2a","order":"03.11.003.19555"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.5"},"2 Ne. 2:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/13.28.27-28"},"Mosiah 13:28 (27–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.2b","order":"03.11.003.19557"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.17"},"Rom. 10:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.5a","order":"03.11.003.19559"},["b","5a"],["span.small","GR"],"grants, furnishes."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.6a","order":"03.11.003.19561"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.7a","order":"03.11.003.19563"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/abrahamic-covenant"},"TG Abrahamic Covenant"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.8a","order":"03.11.003.19565"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heathen"},"TG Heathen"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.8b","order":"03.11.003.19567"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gospel"},"TG Gospel"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.8c","order":"03.11.003.19569"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-mission-of"},"TG Israel, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"8d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.8d","order":"03.11.003.19571"},["b","8d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mission-of-latter-day-saints"},"TG Mission of Latter-day Saints"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.9a","order":"03.11.003.19573"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-blessings-of"},"TG Israel, Blessings of"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.10a","order":"03.11.003.19575"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"TG Curse"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.11a","order":"03.11.003.19577"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.13a","order":"03.11.003.19579"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/4.5"},"Gal. 4:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.13b","order":"03.11.003.19581"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bondage-spiritual"},"TG Bondage, Spiritual"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"Curse"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.13c","order":"03.11.003.19583"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/42.22.1-28"},"Alma 42:22 (1–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.13d","order":"03.11.003.19585"},["b","13d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/21.23"},"Deut. 21:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.14a","order":"03.11.003.19587"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/blessing"},"TG Blessing"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-mission-of"},"Israel, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.14b","order":"03.11.003.19589"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/8.35.29-35"},"Acts 8:35 (29–35)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.14c","order":"03.11.003.19591"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/promise"},"TG Promise"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.16a","order":"03.11.003.19593"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/132.11"},"Ps. 132:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.55.54-55"},"Luke 1:55 (54–55)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.16b","order":"03.11.003.19595"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.40"},"D&C 107:40"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.17a","order":"03.11.003.19597"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-bondage-of-in-egypt"},"TG Israel, Bondage of, in Egypt"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.18a","order":"03.11.003.19599"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/inheritance"},"TG Inheritance"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.19a","order":"03.11.003.19601"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-gal/3.19-20"},["span.small","JST"],"Gal. 3:19–20 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.19b","order":"03.11.003.19603"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/1.9"},"1 Tim. 1:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.22a","order":"03.11.003.19605"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/49.8"},"D&C 49:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.24a","order":"03.11.003.19607"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/law-of-moses"},"TG Law of Moses"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.24b","order":"03.11.003.19609"},["b","24b"],["span.small","GR"],"pedagogue, director, supervisor of children.",["span.small","JST"],"Gal. 3:24 … schoolmaster",["i","until"],"Christ …",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-anticipation"},"TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Anticipation"],"."],["div",{"id":"24c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.24c","order":"03.11.003.19611"},["b","24c"],"See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.16a"},["span.small","JST"],"Rom. 4:16 (Rom. 4:16 note",["i","a"],")"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.32.32-33"},"Moro. 10:32 (32–33)"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.26a","order":"03.11.003.19613"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sons-and-daughters-of-god"},"TG Sons and Daughters of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.26b","order":"03.11.003.19615"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/baptism-qualifications-for"},"TG Baptism, Qualifications for"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.27a","order":"03.11.003.19617"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/13.14"},"Rom. 13:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.13.12-13"},"2 Ne. 31:13 (12–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/5.8.2-14"},"Mosiah 5:8 (2–14)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/baptism"},"TG Baptism"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.28a","order":"03.11.003.19619"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gentiles"},"TG Gentiles"],"."],["div",{"id":"28b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.28b","order":"03.11.003.19621"},["b","28b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.12.12-13"},"Rom. 10:12 (12–13)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unity"},"TG Unity"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.29a","order":"03.11.003.19623"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conversion"},"TG Conversion"],"."],["div",{"id":"29b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.29b","order":"03.11.003.19625"},["b","29b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seed-of-abraham"},"TG Seed of Abraham"],"."],["div",{"id":"29c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.29c","order":"03.11.003.19627"},["b","29c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/4.28"},"Gal. 4:28"],"."]]}
